00:01:40.490 --> 00:01:42.260 align:middle line:84%
And you mentioned
it as relationship

00:01:42.260 --> 00:01:47.277 align:middle line:84%
as practice in spirituality
or spiritual practice,

00:01:47.277 --> 00:01:48.860 align:middle line:84%
how we can work with
our relationships

00:01:48.860 --> 00:01:50.280 align:middle line:90%
from that perspective.

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:53.030 align:middle line:84%
And we have so many that
are painful, so many

00:01:53.030 --> 00:01:56.120 align:middle line:84%
that are addictive, and that
have a negative aspect to them,

00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:57.840 align:middle line:84%
but they don't have
