00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:59.410 align:middle line:90%
They should not be.

00:01:59.410 --> 00:02:03.050 align:middle line:84%
>> No, it seems that
relationships are a great

00:02:03.050 --> 00:02:07.700 align:middle line:84%
