00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:23.600 align:middle line:84%
it seems that love can turn
into hate in relationships.

00:02:23.600 --> 00:02:26.610 align:middle line:90%
It can happen within a second.

00:02:26.610 --> 00:02:29.960 align:middle line:84%
