00:11:51.200 --> 00:11:53.330 align:middle line:10%
can really assist
you in becoming

00:11:53.330 --> 00:11:55.360 align:middle line:10%
a healthy, balanced person.

00:11:55.360 --> 00:11:58.400 align:middle line:84%
As you know, stress is what
makes our lives so difficult

00:11:58.400 --> 00:11:59.690 align:middle line:90%
and can bring on illness.

00:11:59.690 --> 00:12:04.520 align:middle line:84%
One technique or practice that
is so profound is surrender.

00:12:04.520 --> 00:12:07.632 align:middle line:84%
It even affects the aging
process, does it not?

00:12:07.632 --> 00:12:14.930 align:middle line:10%
>> Yes, surrender is acceptance
of this moment as it is

00:12:14.930 --> 00:12:18.380 align:middle line:10%
because you realized the
futility of that state of inner

00:12:18.380 --> 00:12:25.400 align:middle line:10%
resistance to what is, to simply
make this moment your friend

00:12:25.400 --> 00:12:26.930 align:middle line:10%
rather than your enemy.

00:12:26.930 --> 00:12:28.460 align:middle line:84%
And then you
realize that perhaps

00:12:28.460 --> 00:12:33.200 align:middle line:84%
for many years, the
now, the present moment,

00:12:33.200 --> 00:12:37.190 align:middle line:84%
you've treated it as an enemy,
trying to get away from it,

00:12:37.190 --> 00:12:41.900 align:middle line:84%
not liking it, constantly
criticizing it.

00:12:41.900 --> 00:12:47.570 align:middle line:84%
So this transformation of
no longer internally trying

00:12:47.570 --> 00:12:52.400 align:middle line:84%
to escape from or deny
the aliveness that

00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:55.040 align:middle line:84%
is in this moment
that also brings

00:12:55.040 --> 00:12:58.160 align:middle line:84%
about a transformation
in the physical body,

00:12:58.160 --> 00:13:03.260 align:middle line:84%
because a lot of the contraction
that people sense, that which

00:13:03.260 --> 00:13:06.150 align:middle line:84%
stops the healthy
flow of life energy

00:13:06.150 --> 00:13:09.560 align:middle line:84%
through the body
what is called chi,

00:13:09.560 --> 00:13:13.610 align:middle line:84%
that which stops that is the
state of fearful contraction

00:13:13.610 --> 00:13:17.630 align:middle line:84%
that is there and how does--
where does that originate,

00:13:17.630 --> 00:13:23.230 align:middle line:84%
it's because you never
embrace this moment as it is.

00:13:23.230 --> 00:13:26.500 align:middle line:84%
You mentally project
yourself forward

00:13:26.500 --> 00:13:29.860 align:middle line:90%
to some possible future moment.

00:13:29.860 --> 00:13:36.640 align:middle line:84%
And in that gap between
now and later, fear arises.

00:13:36.640 --> 00:13:39.550 align:middle line:84%
The fear makes
the body contract,

00:13:39.550 --> 00:13:43.100 align:middle line:84%
and that greatly impedes
the flow of life energy

00:13:43.100 --> 00:13:43.900 align:middle line:90%
through the body.

00:13:43.900 --> 00:13:47.120 align:middle line:84%
>> You mentioned continue
to say yes, say yes to life,

00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:49.780 align:middle line:84%
say yes to now, say yes
to what is going on.

00:13:49.780 --> 00:13:52.690 align:middle line:84%
It really is a matter
of acceptance and going

00:13:52.690 --> 00:13:55.250 align:middle line:84%
with, kind of, the
flow of your life.

00:13:55.250 --> 00:13:59.770 align:middle line:84%
And if you are in fear, then
that's when the blockages come.

00:13:59.770 --> 00:14:02.240 align:middle line:90%
But the acceptance of the now.

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:04.160 align:middle line:90%
OK, so we accept it.

00:14:04.160 --> 00:14:06.380 align:middle line:90%
We actually embrace it.

00:14:06.380 --> 00:14:12.430 align:middle line:84%
>> The now and life are one
because there is no life

00:14:12.430 --> 00:14:14.440 align:middle line:90%
outside of now.

00:14:14.440 --> 00:14:18.220 align:middle line:84%
So when you look at it, most
people live in past and future,

00:14:18.220 --> 00:14:22.870 align:middle line:84%
rarely in the now, so they live
in a conceptualized universe

00:14:22.870 --> 00:14:26.710 align:middle line:84%
because now is
all there ever is.

00:14:26.710 --> 00:14:28.840 align:middle line:84%
Nothing ever
happened in the past.

00:14:28.840 --> 00:14:30.250 align:middle line:90%
It happened in the now.

00:14:30.250 --> 00:14:32.360 align:middle line:84%
Nothing will ever
happen in the future.

00:14:32.360 --> 00:14:34.180 align:middle line:90%
It will happen the now.

00:14:34.180 --> 00:14:36.760 align:middle line:84%
So when you realize
how vital it is,

00:14:36.760 --> 00:14:42.960 align:middle line:84%
then you open yourself up to
an enormous power that is here

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:45.930 align:middle line:84%
all the time that
you cut yourself

00:14:45.930 --> 00:14:50.730 align:middle line:84%
off from when you live in and
through mental projections

00:14:50.730 --> 00:14:53.880 align:middle line:84%
of past and, for many
people, future, mostly.

00:14:53.880 --> 00:14:55.710 align:middle line:90%
>> Now a lot of people will--

00:14:55.710 --> 00:14:57.960 align:middle line:84%
oh, maybe they'll do astrology,
or they'll do I Ching,

00:14:57.960 --> 00:14:59.520 align:middle line:84%
or they'll do the
tarot, or they will

00:14:59.520 --> 00:15:01.250 align:middle line:90%
do some form of divination.

00:15:01.250 --> 00:15:04.205 align:middle line:84%
And is it because they really
are not satisfied or not living

00:15:04.205 --> 00:15:06.330 align:middle line:84%
in the now, and they're
projecting into the future,

00:15:06.330 --> 00:15:07.955 align:middle line:84%
they want to see what
the future holds?

00:15:07.955 --> 00:15:11.190 align:middle line:84%
Is it either dissatisfaction
with what is?

00:15:11.190 --> 00:15:12.910 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, they want
to, in some way,

00:15:12.910 --> 00:15:16.410 align:middle line:84%
perhaps control what is
going to happen to them.

00:15:16.410 --> 00:15:17.550 align:middle line:90%
They want to know--

00:15:17.550 --> 00:15:20.480 align:middle line:84%
but, of course, if you knew
what is going to happen to you,

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:23.560 align:middle line:84%
your life would lose
all sense of adventure.

00:15:23.560 --> 00:15:26.160 align:middle line:84%
It would-- everything
would be totally fixed.

00:15:26.160 --> 00:15:30.780 align:middle line:84%
So it's simply-- the most
powerful spiritual practice

00:15:30.780 --> 00:15:34.905 align:middle line:90%
is the practice of now.

00:15:34.905 --> 00:15:37.500 align:middle line:84%
>> Be in the moment as
the Sufi master would say.

00:15:37.500 --> 00:15:38.460 align:middle line:90%
That's why they dance.

00:15:38.460 --> 00:15:39.300 align:middle line:90%
That's why they whirl.

00:15:39.300 --> 00:15:40.550 align:middle line:90%
It brings you into the moment.

00:15:40.550 --> 00:15:42.750 align:middle line:84%
And there are practices
that do that now.

00:15:42.750 --> 00:15:43.830 align:middle line:90%
Some of the things--

00:15:43.830 --> 00:15:47.430 align:middle line:84%
one thing that you suggested
was the inner body.

00:15:47.430 --> 00:15:49.560 align:middle line:84%
And tell me about
that and how people

00:15:49.560 --> 00:15:53.910 align:middle line:84%
can come from the inner
body and come into the now,

00:15:53.910 --> 00:15:55.110 align:middle line:90%
be in the now.

00:15:55.110 --> 00:15:59.790 align:middle line:84%
>> Most people are cut off from
the aliveness of their body

00:15:59.790 --> 00:16:03.420 align:middle line:84%
because all their attention
is absorbed continuously

00:16:03.420 --> 00:16:05.350 align:middle line:90%
by thought processes there.

00:16:05.350 --> 00:16:08.640 align:middle line:84%
In other words, they're
completely in the head.

00:16:08.640 --> 00:16:12.480 align:middle line:84%
That center of gravity, so
to speak, is in the mind,

00:16:12.480 --> 00:16:14.330 align:middle line:84%
in their continuous
stream of thinking.

00:16:14.330 --> 00:16:16.560 align:middle line:84%
And what are they
thinking about?

00:16:16.560 --> 00:16:19.050 align:middle line:84%
Probably the next
moment, the future.

00:16:19.050 --> 00:16:20.640 align:middle line:84%
They're projecting
themselves forward,

00:16:20.640 --> 00:16:23.280 align:middle line:84%
trying to control
it in some way,

00:16:23.280 --> 00:16:26.170 align:middle line:84%
trying to prevent certain
things from happening,

00:16:26.170 --> 00:16:31.140 align:middle line:84%
and so they lose themselves
in the mind and in time,

00:16:31.140 --> 00:16:32.640 align:middle line:90%
in future.

00:16:32.640 --> 00:16:39.780 align:middle line:84%
So a very powerful practice
is to bring your attention

00:16:39.780 --> 00:16:43.950 align:middle line:84%
from the head into
the body and to feel

00:16:43.950 --> 00:16:47.550 align:middle line:84%
the aliveness that
is always present

00:16:47.550 --> 00:16:50.440 align:middle line:90%
throughout your entire body.

00:16:50.440 --> 00:16:52.500 align:middle line:84%
And it can start
with a simple thing,

00:16:52.500 --> 00:16:57.090 align:middle line:84%
like sensing the aliveness
that is in your hand.

00:16:57.090 --> 00:17:01.980 align:middle line:84%
And at first, some people say,
well, I can't feel anything.

00:17:01.980 --> 00:17:04.950 align:middle line:84%
And I sometimes point
out, yes, you can.

00:17:04.950 --> 00:17:08.369 align:middle line:84%
Just close your eyes,
hold up your right hand,

00:17:08.369 --> 00:17:10.957 align:middle line:84%
and without moving your hand
and without looking at it,

00:17:10.957 --> 00:17:13.290 align:middle line:84%
is there any way you can know
whether your right hand is

00:17:13.290 --> 00:17:14.530 align:middle line:90%
still there?

00:17:14.530 --> 00:17:17.040 align:middle line:84%
And then they do that,
and suddenly, they

00:17:17.040 --> 00:17:21.599 align:middle line:84%
can feel the energy
in their right hand.

00:17:21.599 --> 00:17:24.660 align:middle line:84%
They can sense it, and
they're beginning now

00:17:24.660 --> 00:17:27.589 align:middle line:84%
to enter the body
with their attention.

00:17:27.589 --> 00:17:31.380 align:middle line:84%
And in the same way that you
can feel the aliveness there,

00:17:31.380 --> 00:17:34.380 align:middle line:84%
you can very easily
feel the aliveness that

00:17:34.380 --> 00:17:37.290 align:middle line:84%
is in the rest of the
body and then sense it

00:17:37.290 --> 00:17:40.920 align:middle line:90%
as a general flow of aliveness.

00:17:40.920 --> 00:17:45.750 align:middle line:84%
Every cell is alive, and that
takes your attention away from

00:17:45.750 --> 00:17:49.500 align:middle line:84%
the mind, and also brings you
into the now because you cannot

00:17:49.500 --> 00:17:53.340 align:middle line:84%
be inhabiting the bodies,
one way of putting it,

00:17:53.340 --> 00:17:57.400 align:middle line:84%
truly inhabiting the body
when you inhabit the body,

00:17:57.400 --> 00:18:01.470 align:middle line:84%
you cannot be away from the now
that is an anchor for staying

00:18:01.470 --> 00:18:06.450 align:middle line:84%
present, and that is a state of
great power because we may not

00:18:06.450 --> 00:18:11.580 align:middle line:84%
realize how much
intelligence is actually--

00:18:11.580 --> 00:18:14.730 align:middle line:84%
how much intelligence
lives in the body

00:18:14.730 --> 00:18:16.840 align:middle line:90%
and in every cell of the body.

00:18:16.840 --> 00:18:20.280 align:middle line:10%
If you had to control
the workings of the body

00:18:20.280 --> 00:18:23.280 align:middle line:10%
through your mind, the body
would break down immediately

00:18:23.280 --> 00:18:25.470 align:middle line:10%
because it's far too complex.

00:18:25.470 --> 00:18:28.780 align:middle line:10%
Only the intelligence in the
body that is in every cell

00:18:28.780 --> 00:18:34.490 align:middle line:10%
and in every organ can make
the body function in that way.

00:18:34.490 --> 00:18:38.370 align:middle line:84%
So the greater intelligence
that is there--

00:18:38.370 --> 00:18:41.000 align:middle line:84%
the one intelligence that is
there of which the human mind

00:18:41.000 --> 00:18:43.280 align:middle line:84%
is only a tiny
aspect, how do you

00:18:43.280 --> 00:18:45.500 align:middle line:84%
connect with that
one intelligence

00:18:45.500 --> 00:18:48.200 align:middle line:90%
that runs the entire universe?

00:18:48.200 --> 00:18:50.210 align:middle line:84%
The easiest way to
connect with that

00:18:50.210 --> 00:18:55.070 align:middle line:84%
is to start by connecting
with your inner body.

00:18:55.070 --> 00:18:58.170 align:middle line:84%
>> Now many people are
suffering with disease.

00:18:58.170 --> 00:19:01.570 align:middle line:10%
And we know that through pain
and through disease and impact

00:19:01.570 --> 00:19:04.040 align:middle line:10%
and trauma, we often do evolve.

00:19:04.040 --> 00:19:08.210 align:middle line:84%
However, how can we transform
illness and suffering?

00:19:08.210 --> 00:19:11.240 align:middle line:84%
What can we do with
the power of now

00:19:11.240 --> 00:19:13.872 align:middle line:84%
to transform illness
and suffering?

00:19:13.872 --> 00:19:19.040 align:middle line:84%
>> If illness is already
there, see that you don't form

00:19:19.040 --> 00:19:22.620 align:middle line:90%
an identity out of your illness.

00:19:22.620 --> 00:19:24.450 align:middle line:84%
You don't make an
identity out of it.

00:19:24.450 --> 00:19:27.980 align:middle line:84%
You identify with it
so much that you--

00:19:27.980 --> 00:19:30.350 align:middle line:84%
the image forms
in your mind of me

00:19:30.350 --> 00:19:34.400 align:middle line:84%
as a person who has that
or is a sufferer of that.

00:19:34.400 --> 00:19:38.210 align:middle line:84%
So simply bring it down to
this moment and the reality

00:19:38.210 --> 00:19:39.380 align:middle line:90%
of this moment.

00:19:39.380 --> 00:19:42.260 align:middle line:84%
So when I speak of
surrendering to an illness,

00:19:42.260 --> 00:19:45.410 align:middle line:84%
I'm not saying surrender to
the fact that you are ill.

00:19:45.410 --> 00:19:47.720 align:middle line:90%
That's a mental image.

00:19:47.720 --> 00:19:52.160 align:middle line:84%
Simply surrender to whatever
this moment presents

00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:54.980 align:middle line:84%
and that maybe at
this moment, pain.

00:19:54.980 --> 00:19:57.230 align:middle line:90%
It may be disability.

00:19:57.230 --> 00:19:59.980 align:middle line:90%
It may be discomfort.

00:19:59.980 --> 00:20:04.540 align:middle line:84%
And an illness can become
your spiritual teacher

00:20:04.540 --> 00:20:09.610 align:middle line:84%
because it can teach you
the state of surrender,

00:20:09.610 --> 00:20:14.290 align:middle line:84%
to say yes to what
is, not to resist it.

00:20:14.290 --> 00:20:17.910 align:middle line:84%
Enormous healing
powers are released

00:20:17.910 --> 00:20:21.630 align:middle line:84%
when you enter the stage
of nonresistance, which

00:20:21.630 --> 00:20:24.150 align:middle line:84%
has nothing to do with
resignation and saying,

00:20:24.150 --> 00:20:26.100 align:middle line:90%
oh, I might just well accept.

00:20:26.100 --> 00:20:27.870 align:middle line:90%
I'm not going to get any better.

00:20:27.870 --> 00:20:29.520 align:middle line:90%
Nothing to do with that.

00:20:29.520 --> 00:20:33.810 align:middle line:84%
You simply accept the
reality of this moment

00:20:33.810 --> 00:20:40.080 align:middle line:84%
as it is without constructing
a mental story on top of it.

00:20:40.080 --> 00:20:44.100 align:middle line:84%
Simply this, the
pain is there, so let

00:20:44.100 --> 00:20:47.430 align:middle line:90%
the pain teach you surrender.

00:20:47.430 --> 00:20:53.670 align:middle line:84%
That's how the egoic
entity, the mind-made self

00:20:53.670 --> 00:20:57.630 align:middle line:84%
can actually become
eroded through an illness,

00:20:57.630 --> 00:20:59.340 align:middle line:90%
and it has happened.

00:20:59.340 --> 00:21:03.850 align:middle line:84%
I have met people who have
had severe disability,

00:21:03.850 --> 00:21:06.750 align:middle line:84%
and they were in
their wheelchair,

00:21:06.750 --> 00:21:11.310 align:middle line:84%
perhaps totally incapacitated,
and I looked into their eyes,

00:21:11.310 --> 00:21:14.940 align:middle line:84%
and there was an enormous
light shining through,

00:21:14.940 --> 00:21:17.220 align:middle line:90%
an enormous aliveness.

00:21:17.220 --> 00:21:19.940 align:middle line:84%
They had surrendered
to their condition.

00:21:19.940 --> 00:21:22.830 align:middle line:84%
And then I met others
in the same condition,

00:21:22.830 --> 00:21:26.280 align:middle line:84%
there was great bitterness
and anger and resentment.

00:21:26.280 --> 00:21:29.110 align:middle line:84%
They were-- they
had closed down.

00:21:29.110 --> 00:21:33.570 align:middle line:84%
And so healing is
more likely to happen,

00:21:33.570 --> 00:21:36.960 align:middle line:84%
much more likely to happen
in the surrendered state.

00:21:36.960 --> 00:21:39.540 align:middle line:84%
>> If that tenseness is
gone, the anger that--

00:21:39.540 --> 00:21:42.780 align:middle line:84%
>> All healing powers
are released in the state

00:21:42.780 --> 00:21:45.140 align:middle line:84%
of openness, that is
the state of surrender,

00:21:45.140 --> 00:21:47.340 align:middle line:84%
because the state of
nonsurrender is the state

00:21:47.340 --> 00:21:53.460 align:middle line:84%
of closeness, shutting down,
contraction, tightness.

00:21:53.460 --> 00:21:55.350 align:middle line:90%
>> So the power of now can be--

00:21:55.350 --> 00:21:59.040 align:middle line:84%
that we can actually put
ourselves in a healing state,

00:21:59.040 --> 00:22:00.300 align:middle line:90%
being open to healing.

00:22:00.300 --> 00:22:05.220 align:middle line:84%
>> Yes, so the power of now is
always connected with working

00:22:05.220 --> 00:22:12.480 align:middle line:84%
with whatever is at this moment,
not demanding that your life

00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:18.660 align:middle line:84%
should be different, not
being antagonistic towards

00:22:18.660 --> 00:22:20.590 align:middle line:90%
the reality of this moment.

00:22:20.590 --> 00:22:21.990 align:middle line:90%
>> Just render to the moment.

00:22:21.990 --> 00:22:23.640 align:middle line:90%
Thank you, Eckhart.

